HEADWORD: Ownership
<hw>Own"er*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being an owner;
the right to own; exclusive right of possession; legal or just claim or
title; proprietorship.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

